1. The Wall Street Journal: Trump's plot to remove Powell has leaked, and the Fed's successor has surfaced;
2. The White House will set up a working group to urgently deal with the crisis of imposing tariffs on China;
3. Trump plans to hold a dinner for TRUMP token holders, and the team is making a webpage for this;
4. Du Jun: ABCDE has stopped investing in new projects and suspending the fundraising plan for the second phase of the fund. The original team will continue to be responsible for the post-investment support of existing projects;
5. Binance has launched KYC re-verification for Indian users to comply with AML regulations;
6. Bank for International Settlements: Cryptocurrency has become a means of transferring wealth from the poor to the rich during market crises;
7. CZ: If the details of Binance's support for KiloEx are fully disclosed, hackers will learn to avoid it;
8. KiloEx: Will jointly release a review of the incident with SlowMist, thank CZ and Binance for their emergency assistance in responding to hacker attacks.
